            <h3 style="color: #ff004f;">Title:Object Counter</h3><br>
            <p style="color: azure;font-size: 27px;">The Object Counter mini project employs a breadboard, buzzer, button, LED, seven-segment display, and an IR sensor, controlled by an IC.
                 It tracks objects through the IR sensor, triggering the LED, buzzer, and displaying the count on the seven-segment display. 
                 A reset button allows for count management. Applications include automated attendance, people counting, inventory tracking, and traffic monitoring, making it a versatile solution for various counting needs in both commercial and public settings.
            </p>
